data.text: Capital - history derives from the Tagalog "may-nila" meaning "where there is indigo" and refers to the presence of indigo-yielding plants growing in the area surrounding the original settlement Capital - time difference UTC+8 (13 hours ahead of Washington, DC, during Standard Time)
